text:
I'm a founding team member at Power Club, a Bangalore based EdTech startup where 11-17 year olds test drive careers to design their dream lives.

We are considering workshops in apartment complexes and offices as a channel to acquire first 100 users.

If you have prior experience in this channel, please guide me how to go about doing that.

title: Show HN: The OS for your physical activity
text:
Steddy is the operating system for your exercise!

Today: A mindblowingly slick to-do list.

5 years from now: The Apple Fitness killer.

Just kidding (but not really). The roadmap goes something like... (1) social layer, follower by (2) video layer.

We'd love to hear what you all think!
